<div class="app-content timeline">
  <div class="content-wrapper">

    <header class="wrap header-main header-design-manual">
      <a class="coop-logo" aria-label="Homepage" href="index.html">
        <img src="assets/images/logos/coop-logo.svg" alt="Co-op">
      </a>
      <span>Sandra</span>
    </header>

    <main id="main" class="main">
      <article class="wrap">
          <div class="row margin-bh">
            <div class="column large-7">
              <section class="widget">
                <div class="card-intro">
                  <h1>Now</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="home-card split">
                  <p>Based on your Membership spending it looks like you often buy fish. Why not try some white wine to go with it? Co-op Littleover has an offer on Co-op Irresistible Premier Cru Chablis. Open until 9pm. <a href="#">Set a reminder</a></p>
                  <figure style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'cru-chablis.png' %>')"></figure>
                </div>
                <a href="#">Hide this</a>
              </section>
              <section class="widget">
                <div class="home-card split">
                  <figure style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'causes.jpg' %>')"></figure>
                  <p>By shopping at Co-op, you’ve raised £3.47 that we’ll give to a local cause. That may not sound like much, but last year Co-op customers like you raised £180 million. <a href="https://membership.coop.co.uk/sign-in">Pick your charity to receive it</a></p>
                </div>
                <a href="#">Hide this</a>
              </section>
              <section class="widget">
                <div class="card-intro">
                  <h1>September</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="home-card form">
                  <div class="page-1">
                    <p>You've told us you're moving home. We can help with that.</p>
                    <label for="postcode">Where are you moving to?</label>
                    <input id="postcode" type="text"><br />
                    <a href="2017-08-08-consent" class="btn btn-primary">Continue</a>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <a href="#">Hide this</a>
              </section>
              <section class="widget">
                <div class="card-intro">
                  <h1>October</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="home-card split">
                  <figure style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'onestep-walkers.jpg' %>')">

                  </figure>
                  <p>Based on your spending we think you might have a dog. There's a 'Onestep Walkers' Meetup in your area. <a href="https://www.meetup.com/ONESTEP-WALKERS-40s-WALKING-GROUP/">Join this Meetup and take your dog along</a>.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="#">Hide this</a>
              </section>
              <section class="widget">
                <div class="home-card split">
                  <p>Washing machine more than eight years old? <a href="https://electrical.coop.co.uk/laundry/washing-machines/">It might be time for a new one</a>.</p>
                  <figure style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'washing-machine.jpg' %>')"></figure>
                </div>
                <a href="#">Hide this</a>
              </section>
              <section class="widget">
                <div class="home-card split">
                  <figure style="background-image: url('<%= image_path 'electric-fire.jpg' %>')"></figure>
                  <p>Sarah is offering to give away an electric fire in Derby. <a href="https://www.streetbank.com/things/115510?locale=en">Do you need one?</a></p>
                </div>
                <a href="#">Hide this</a>
              </section>
            </div>
          </div>
      </article>
    </main>

  </div>
</div>

